Title: Congratulating Urologic Surgeon Dr. Paul M. Russo as both a 2018 Top Doctor and a 2018 Outstanding Teacher at Memorial Sloan Kettering Cancer Center
ActClause: LEGISLATIVE RESOLUTION congratulating Dr. Paul Russo upon the occasion of being named a 2018 Top Doctor, and the recipient of the 2018 Outstanding Teacher of the Year Award after many years of distinguished service as a Urologic Surgeon at Sidney Kimmel Center, Memorial Sloan Kettering Cancer Center
